Package jmud.command

Class Summary
Commands Represents a command to send the client all available commands.
CommandTemplate Abstract command class for implementing all commands.
Look Represents a command to look at rooms or entities.
Quit Represents a command to disconnect from the server.
Say Represents a command to say a message in the player's current room.
